---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Enclosed Car Transport | Premium Vehicle Protection';
const description =
  'Maximum protection for your luxury, vintage, or classic car. Our enclosed car transport ensures your vehicle arrives in pristine condition. Get a quote today.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <section
    class="relative bg-[var(--color-primary-900)] text-white pt-24 pb-32 overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-primary-950)]/90 to-[var(--color-primary-900)]/50 z-10"
      >
      </div>
      {/* Abstract background pattern or image could go here */}
      <svg
        class="w-full h-full text-[var(--color-primary-800)]"
        fill="currentColor"
        viewBox="0 0 100 100"
        preserveAspectRatio="none"
      >
        <path d="M0 100 C 20 0 50 0 100 100 Z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[var(--color-accent-500)]/10 text-[var(--color-accent-500)] px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 border border-[var(--color-accent-500)]/20"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg
          >
          Maximum Protection
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">
          Enclosed Car <br />
          <span
            class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-accent-400)] to-[var(--color-accent-600)]"
            >Transport Services</span
          >
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-xl text-[var(--color-neutral-400)] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10"
        >
          The ultimate safe transport solution for your luxury, vintage, or
          sentimental vehicle. Security, privacy, and protection from the
          elements.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="https://ratecheck.movingcars.com.au/quote/v2"
            class="bg-[var(--color-accent-500)] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-400)] text-[var(--color-primary-950)] font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-[var(--color-accent-500)]/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            Get a Quote Now
          </a>
          <a
            href="#more-info"
            class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all backdrop-blur-sm"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Cost Warning / Strategy Block */}
  <section class="py-16 -mt-16 relative z-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-[var(--color-neutral-100)] max-w-5xl mx-auto"
      >
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div
            class="shrink-0 bg-[var(--color-primary-50)] p-4 rounded-2xl text-[var(--color-primary-600)]"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-8 h-8"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-primary-900)] mb-4">
              Important Cost Advice
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-600)] leading-relaxed mb-6">
              We have found that due to the much higher than expected costs of
              Enclosed Vehicle Transport, we ask that customers <strong
                >obtain a standard quote first</strong
              >. Once received, if you wish to upgrade to a fully enclosed
              service, simply reply to our quote and request upgrade rates.
            </p>
            <div
              class="bg-[var(--color-neutral-50)] p-6 rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-neutral-200)]"
            >
              <h4
                class="font-bold text-[var(--color-primary-800)] mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide"
              >
                Did you know?
              </h4>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-600)] text-sm">
                More often than not, it is fully enclosed only on linehaul or
                long-distance. Meaning if you live in the suburbs of Sydney, a
                standard non-enclosed truck will collect your vehicle, but once
                it starts to move across the country, instructions are strictly
                enclosed.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main id="more-info" class="bg-[var(--color-neutral-50)] py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      {/* Intro Content */}
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--color-primary-900)] mb-6"
        >
          Australia's Trusted Enclosed Specialist
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-neutral-600)] leading-relaxed">
          Over the years, Moving Cars has established itself as a leading
          enclosed vehicle transport company by offering fast, secure, and
          excellent car transport solutions across Australia's length and
          breadth without burning a hole in your pocket.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Features Grid */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-24">
        {
          [
            {
              title: 'Luxury Cars',
              icon: 'M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z',
            },
            {
              title: 'Vintage Classics',
              icon: 'M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z',
            },
            { title: 'Sports Vehicles', icon: 'M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z' },
            {
              title: 'Prototype Cars',
              icon: 'M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z',
            },
            {
              title: 'Racing Vehicles',
              icon: 'M3 21v-8a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8M15 3h6v6M9 3H3v6M9 21h6M9 3v18M15 3v18',
            },
            {
              title: 'Boats & Trailers',
              icon: 'M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z',
            },
          ].map((feature) => (
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-[var(--color-neutral-100)] hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[var(--color-accent-500)]/10 text-[var(--color-accent-600)] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d={feature.icon}
                  />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-[var(--color-primary-900)] mb-2">
                {feature.title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-neutral-500)] text-sm">
                Specialized handling and care for your{' '}
                {feature.title.toLowerCase()}.
              </p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      {/* Detailed Content Sections */}
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-24">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-primary-900)] mb-6">
            Fully Customized Enclosed Carriers
          </h3>
          <div
            class="space-y-6 text-[var(--color-neutral-600)] leading-relaxed"
          >
            <p>
              Our fleet of covered car transporters is driven by professional,
              licensed, and insured drivers who care for your vehicle like their
              own. These carriers are equipped with specialized hydraulics that
              ensure minimal manual handling and maximum security.
            </p>
            <div
              class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[var(--color-accent-500)] shadow-sm"
            >
              <h4 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-primary-800)] mb-1">
                Hydraulic Liftgates
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm">
                During loading, your vehicle remains horizontal to avoid damage,
                dents, or scratches. Our advanced hydraulic liftgates ensure
                stability from pickup to delivery.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[var(--color-primary-400)] shadow-sm"
            >
              <h4 class="font-bold text-[var(--color-primary-800)] mb-1">
                Unmatched Security
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm">
                Includes GPS tracking for updates, round-the-clock security at
                storage facilities, and background-checked staff for your peace
                of mind.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div
            class="bg-[var(--color-neutral-200)] rounded-[2.5rem] aspect-square relative overflow-hidden"
          >
            {/* Image Placeholder */}
            <div
              class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-[var(--color-neutral-400)]"
            >
              <span class="font-bold text-lg">Premium Carrier Image</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Why Choose Us / CTA */}
      <div
        class="bg-[var(--color-primary-900)] text-white rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-20 opacity-5">
          <svg class="w-64 h-64" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path d="M12 2L4.5 20.29l.71.71L12 18l6.79 3 .71-.71z"></path></svg
          >
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-8 relative z-10">
          Is Open Car Transport Safe?
        </h2>
        <div
          class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 relative z-10 text-[var(--color-neutral-300)] leading-relaxed space-y-4"
        >
          <p>
            For the most part, yes. Open transport is safe and widely used.
            However, it doesn't offer complete protection against natural wear
            and tear, dust, debris, and harsh weather conditions.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you have a <strong>prized possession</strong> that needs to arrive
            showroom-ready, enclosed transport is the only choice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://ratecheck.movingcars.com.au/quote/v2"
          class="relative z-10 inline-block bg-[var(--color-accent-500)] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-400)] text-[var(--color-primary-950)] font-black py-5 px-10 rounded-2xl text-xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl"
        >
          Get Your Secure Quote
        </a>
        <p
          class="mt-6 text-[var(--color-neutral-400)] text-sm font-medium relative z-10"
        >
          Free Instant Quotes • No Obligation • 20+ Years Experience
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
